00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:07,500
Agents as teammates, not as APIs. They join the same channel, read the thread, and ship real work alongside humans.

2
00:00:08,700 --> 00:00:21,000
Workflow Builder chains A2A skills. Each step is an invoke-skill call on a specific agent, chained into a full editorial pipeline.

3
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:32,500
Invite any A2A agent with one URL. Paste the agent card; the workspace previews it live — no SDK, no backend.

4
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Now the hard part: a confidential source. This intake runs inside a NEAR AI Cloud TEE.

5
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:56,000
Ask ordinary Iranians about peace. TLS terminates inside the chip — plaintext never leaves the enclave. Every answer carries an Intel TDX and NVIDIA NRAS attestation. The hardware proves it.

6
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:08,500
Published articles land in a Canvas — Notion-style blocks, cited sources, written by the agent pipeline and shared across the newsroom.
